{{Quote|You know the Bruvian saying, 'Kuuta velomin'? 'Seize the moment.' It's all we have. The past is gone, the future may never arrive. What exists is now.|Tolk le Trene, to Jos Vondar|<ref name="MS1">''[[MedStar I: Battle Surgeons]]''</ref>}}
'''Bruvians''' were a social group<ref name="MS1" /> that shared their name with the [[Bruvia system/Legends|Bruvia system]] of the [[Expansion Region/Legends|Expansion Region's]] [[Harron Marches/Legends|Harron Marches]].<ref name="EAOC">{{SW|url=news/star-wars-the-essential-atlas-online-companion|text=''Star Wars: The Essential Atlas'' Online Companion|int=Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion}}</ref> The saying ''Kuuta velomin''&mdash;translating to [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Galactic Basic Standard]] as "Seize the moment"&mdash;was Bruvian in origin.<ref name="MS1" />

